OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be mostly dry on Monday
OL,6,Fwith some sunshine, especially first
OL,7,Fthing, but clouding over with some
OL,8,Fpatchy rain for the Isles in the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Southerly winds will
OL,10,Fstrengthen through the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThe odd spot of rain possible
OL,13,Fin the north at first, otherwise dry
OL,14,Fwith largely clear skies. The odd
OL,15,Fshower possible in the west around
OL,16,Fdawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
