OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FMostly sunny start but chance
OL,6,Fof the odd shower. Rain reaching the
OL,7,Fwest in the afternoon, some heavy,
OL,8,Fcontinuing east though the evening.
OL,9,FWarm in the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMostly
OL,12,Fdry, bright on Wednesday, then rain in
OL,13,Fthe evening. Cooler with sunny
OL,14,Fintervals and showers on Thursday.
OL,15,FTurning wet and windy on Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
